name: Feather Leggings
description:
Printed on Womens Alternative Apparel Crop Leggings.  These feature Peacock Feather design on lower back of each leg.  Available in black with grey/blue screen printed design.  

SHIPPING: All orders within the United States will be shipped USPS in 5-10 business days. 

RETURNS/EXCHANGES: Item must be returned within 30 days of order.  Item must be recieved in original condition (not washed, with original tags attached) and shipped at buyers expense.  Please include note with request for either refund less shipping charges or exchange.  

CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Take care of your leggings and it will they care of you...  Turn inside out and mashine or hand wash.  Hang dry or put in dryer on air only (NO HEAT, LEGGINGS WILL SHRINK).
